                            <comment id="17302881" author="emilles" created="Tue, 16 Mar 2021 20:45:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In static context, &quot;this&quot; refers to the enclosing class as does &quot;owner&quot; within the closure.&#160; Either should produce an error.&#160; Using &quot;delegate&quot; or &quot;it&quot; should work fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
